      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, keeping it garage-kept and professionally detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
