    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a definitive driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically superlative, with a documented VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement already completed. The chassis remains rigid and responsive, benefiting from a proactive rear subframe reinforcement utilizing Turner Motorsport plates. Performance is optimized via individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring peak power delivery and corner-exit traction. The Carbon Black Metallic paint retains its deep luster, while the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and structural integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
