    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and looks exactly as it did on the delivery floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or wear, the carpets are spotless, and the dashboard remains factory-fresh with no UV fading. Every technological feature and interior control operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a complete, chronological service portfolio performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life of fair-weather driving only. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence that drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it was manufactured. All original keys, manuals, and window stickers are included.",
